title: User query: Plan description from client LLM
log: Create a Wayang plan for a query that finds the top 3 highest-revenue orders for the market segment ‘AUTOMOBILE’. Revenue is defined as the sum of l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) per order. The system must join the customer, orders, and lineitem tables using c_custkey = o_custkey and l_orderkey = o_orderkey. Filter orders so that o_orderdate is earlier than 1995-03-15 and l_shipdate is later than 1995-03-15. Group the results by l_orderkey, o_orderdate, and o_shippriority. Then compute total revenue per order, and return only the first 3 rows. Output the result in a textfile.

operations.table: (SELECT c_custkey, c_mktsegment FROM customer) as X
(SELECT o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate, o_shippriority FROM orders) as X

operations.udf: (t: (Int, (Int, Int, String, Int))) => { val order = t._2; (order._1.asInstanceOf[Int], order._3.toString, order._4.asInstanceOf[Int]) }

operations.table: (SELECT l_orderkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_shipdate FROM lineitem) as X

operations.udf: (a: ((Int, String, Int), Double), b: ((Int, String, Int), Double)) => (a._1, a._2 + b._2)
(a: Seq[((Int, String, Int), Double)], b: Seq[((Int, String, Int), Double)]) => { val merged = (a ++ b).sortWith((x,y) => x._2 > y._2); merged.take(3) }

log.thoughts: Filter customers for AUTOMOBILE, join with orders filtered by date, join with lineitems filtered by ship date, compute per-line revenue, aggregate by order key/orderdate/shippriority, then globally keep top 3 by revenue and output to text file.

title: Class: PlanMapper Mapped plan finalized for execution

data.table: (SELECT c_custkey, c_mktsegment FROM (SELECT c_custkey, c_mktsegment FROM customer) as X) as X
(SELECT o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate, o_shippriority FROM (SELECT o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate, o_shippriority FROM orders) as X) as X

data.udf: (t: (Int, (Int, Int, String, Int))) => { val order = t._2; (order._1.asInstanceOf[Int], order._3.toString, order._4.asInstanceOf[Int]) }

data.table: (SELECT l_orderkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_shipdate FROM (SELECT l_orderkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_shipdate FROM lineitem) as X) as X

data.udf: (a: ((Int, String, Int), Double), b: ((Int, String, Int), Double)) => (a._1, a._2 + b._2)
(a: Seq[((Int, String, Int), Double)], b: Seq[((Int, String, Int), Double)]) => { val merged = (a ++ b).sortWith((x,y) => x._2 > y._2); merged.take(3) }

Err: Wayang error. Plan executed unsucessful
